title: Philips Pasta & Noodle Maker - Which Pasta & Noodle maker is for me?
description: Enjoy fresh pasta & noodles in less than 18 minutes, the Philips Pasta and Noodle Maker will automatically mix, knead and extrude your pasta. Bring variety to the table! The pasta & noodle maker comes with 3 to 7 shaping discs  inculding discs for penne, spaghetti and fettuccine. .
